tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [{ title: 'Search' }],
}

phase('Search')
const result = await agent(
  `Execute the semantic search workflow defined in workflows/semantic-search.md.

The working directory is /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

Search query: "Bean ValidationのFormクラスの単体テストを書きたい。テストクラスの作り方とテストデータの準備方法を教えてほしい（目的: テストを書きたい）"

Follow the semantic-search.md workflow exactly. Return the full result including selected_sections array with file paths, section IDs, and relevance levels (high/partial).

For each page you consider, record whether you selected or skipped it and why.
For each section you consider, record whether you selected it (high/partial) or skipped it and why.

Return a JSON object with:
{
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path to knowledge file>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "high|partial", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "selected_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "excluded_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ]
}`,
  {
    label: 'semantic-search',
    phase: 'Search',
    schema: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        selected_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
          }
        },
        selected_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
          }
        }
      },
      required: ['selected_sections', 'selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'excluded_sections']
    }
  }
)

return result
